About Us

Our love of brioche began in 1945 in a French boulangerie, where our family began creating delicious artisanal brioche. Nestled in the countryside of western France, we passed down our family recipes, mastering the perfect brioche: a soft, fluffy, slightly sweet bread that brings joy with every bite.

For four generations, we’ve been baking wholesome brioche breads in France and today, we are delighted to bring our classic French bread to households across Australia. Our original family recipes remain true, and so does our passion for our craft, which inspires every brioche we bake today.

Description: Brioche Gourmet Brioche Burger Buns.These light and buttery Brioche Buns are the ultimate burger buns to create the best tasting burger. All you need to do is add a burger and your favourite filling!These buns are perfect alternative to bread rolls. For a gourmet treat, fill with barbequed meat, salads or cold cuts. About Us.Our love of brioche began in 1945 in a French boulangerie, where our family began creating delicious artisanal brioche. Nestled in the countryside of western France, we passed down our family recipes, mastering the perfect brioche: a soft, fluffy, slightly sweet bread that brings joy with every bite. For four generations, we’ve been baking wholesome brioche breads in France and today, we are delighted to bring our classic French bread to households across Australia. Our original family recipes remain true, and so does our passion for our craft, which inspires every brioche we bake today.

About Us

Our love of brioche began in 1945 in a French boulangerie, where our family began creating delicious artisanal brioche. Nestled in the countryside of western France, we passed down our family recipes, mastering the perfect brioche: a soft, fluffy, slightly sweet bread that brings joy with every bite.

For four generations, we’ve been baking wholesome brioche breads in France and today, we are delighted to bring our classic French bread to households across Australia. Our original family recipes remain true, and so does our passion for our craft, which inspires every brioche we bake today.

Description:
Bill's Organic Sourdough Multi Fruit is a great source of antioxidants.

Bill's certified organic stoneground multifruit sourdough is simply unique. Packed with antioxidant goodness from certified organic sultanas, raisins, figs and apricots, all naturally preserved without sulphites. Sulphites can affect some asthmatics and can be the cause of allergies and sensitivities. A delicious combination of sourdough and fruit - but best of all tastes amazing!

At Bill's, we're focused on inspiring healthier living through healthier choices. All of our delicious sourdoughs are made using pure, natural ingredients from certified organic farms, milling our flour in a traditional stoneguard method, and allowing our unique natural starter to slowly ferment over 18 hours. Simple. Certified Organic and no nasties.

Why 'Certified' Organic? Because we believe it is absolutely essential when creating our highly nutritious and tasty sourdoughs. When you purchase certified organic produce you can be guaranteed (through strict external regular auditing by Australian Certified Organic from farm to plate) that what you're eating is free from harmful artificial fertilisers and chemicals as well as promoting ethical farming practices.
